## Spring Security

### 設定
```java
@Configuration
@EnableWebSecurity
public class SecurityConfig {
    @Bean
    public SecurityFilterChain filterChain(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {
        http
            .csrf(csrf -> csrf.disable())
            .authorizeHttpRequests(auth -> auth
                .requestMatchers("/api/public/**").permitAll()
                .requestMatchers("/api/admin/**").hasRole("ADMIN")
                .anyRequest().authenticated()
            )
            .oauth2ResourceServer(oauth -> oauth.jwt());
        return http.build();
    }
}
```

### JWT 驗證
```java
@RestController
public class ProfileController {
    @GetMapping("/api/me")
    public Map<String, Object> me(@AuthenticationPrincipal Jwt jwt) {
        return Map.of(
            "userId", jwt.getSubject(),
            "email", jwt.getClaim("email")
        );
    }
}
```

## JPA Query

### Repository 方法名
```java
public interface UserRepository extends JpaRepository<User, Long> {
    List<User> findByRole(String role);
    List<User> findByCreatedAtAfter(LocalDateTime date);
    Optional<User> findFirstByEmailIgnoreCase(String email);
}
```

Spring 自動產 SQL。

### 自訂 query
```java
@Query("SELECT u FROM User u WHERE u.email = :email AND u.active = true")
Optional<User> findActiveByEmail(@Param("email") String email);
```

### Native SQL
```java
@Query(value = "SELECT * FROM users WHERE ...", nativeQuery = true)
List<User> customQuery();
```

## Transaction
```java
@Service
public class OrderService {
    @Transactional
    public Order createOrder(OrderRequest req) {
        Order order = orderRepo.save(new Order(...));
        paymentService.charge(req.amount);
        notificationService.sendEmail(req.userEmail);
        return order;
    }
}
```

任一步失敗 → 全 rollback。

## 心法
- Spring Security 強但複雜、用範本起步
- JPA 方便但要懂 N+1 問題
- Transaction 別亂用 @Transactional
- Production 開 SQL log 找慢查

